---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 py-24 px-6 transition-colors duration-300">
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
		<!-- Testimonios Reales -->
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20">
			<div class="p-8 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
				<div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-4">
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
				</div>
				<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 italic mb-6">"Excelente atención en la sucursal Vista Hermosa. El proceso de agendar por la web fue super rápido."</p>
				<p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">— María Rodriguez</p>
			</div>
			<div class="p-8 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
				<div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-4">
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
				</div>
				<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 italic mb-6">"Me atendieron de madrugada en López Portillo. Muy profesionales y equipo de primera."</p>
				<p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">— Juan Carlos T.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="p-8 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800">
				<div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-4">
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
					<Icon name="lucide:star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
				</div>
				<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 italic mb-6">"Los resultados de laboratorio en Villa Esmeralda me llegaron directo a mi celular. Gran sistema."</p>
				<p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">— Laura Salinas</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center md:items-start gap-16 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 pt-16">
			
			<!-- Izquierda: Autoridad -->
			<div class="text-center md:text-left">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4 italic">
					Medic's <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Clínicas Express</span>
				</h2>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
					<div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold text-sm">
						<Icon name="lucide:shield-check" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" />
						Médicos Certificados ante la COFEPRIS
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold text-sm">
						<Icon name="lucide:check-circle" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" />
						Infraestructura Médica de Vanguardia
					</div>
				</div>
				<p class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 text-xs mt-8">
					&copy; 2026 Medic's Clínicas Express. Todos los derechos reservados.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Centro: Navegación -->
			<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
				<p class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs mb-2">Explora</p>
				<nav class="flex gap-8 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold text-sm">
					<a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Inicio</a>
					<a href="/#sucursales" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Sucursales</a>
					<a href="/privacidad" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Privacidad</a>
				</nav>
			</div>

			<!-- Derecha: Social y Créditos -->
			<div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-end gap-6">
				<div class="flex gap-6 text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500">
					<a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors"><Icon name="lucide:facebook" class="w-6 h-6" /></a>
					<a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors"><Icon name="lucide:instagram" class="w-6 h-6" /></a>
					<a href="#" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors"><Icon name="lucide:mail" class="w-6 h-6" /></a>
				</div>
				<p class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium">
					Desarrollado por <a href="https://github.com/said" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold hover:underline">Said Dev</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
